c=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4af2dca9014bd17a7e45c4fb425211ad88ed3f","tid":46112,"uid":14705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T19:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n<br />\n以前佢仲向過我表白<br />\n<br />\n但果時細膽唔敢接受就拒絕左<br />\n<br />\n而家周不時都好掛住佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame 好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83aa6604884d6c43c366043e2d1d04366af7985b","tid":46112,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會 grad左之後先有fd同我講返原來個陣佢都鍾意我 咁就錯過左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之後好好珍惜喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a2d77ea164f26d7de1e649a49e4cb653261fa5","tid":46112,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>grad左就黎2年，之前撞翻曖昧對象(因為某d原因不歡而散)<br />\n雖然曖昧過，但只有我鍾意佢，我知佢唔鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撞翻之後周不時都諗起佢，明明都已經過左3年<br />\n而家我就清楚我冇放低佢，只係收埋左d感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我未撞過，可能係雖然住同一區 但一個住喺北一個住喺南掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf63b4a0a4825888a7a14ea21d3fc8d510c8426","tid":46112,"uid":43427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:29:53.000Z","msg":"想念是會呼吸的痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71cc8a9f32f424fa807af6213e91075d655a9ce","tid":46112,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想念是會呼吸的痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呢幾日無啦啦記返起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247de354e20810ae2ed2054667ed8227e6c253b0","tid":46112,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:04:32.000Z","msg":"點解唔搵人"},{"pid":"e56d70c0d484a66325cbf098482ab371b5bf9feb","tid":46112,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:06:42.000Z","msg":"有呀 不過其實佢唔識我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係知我係邊個<br />\n佢有拍拖 中五開始拍到而家已經5年<br />\n近排撞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝佢幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743c5a5815319d718c759388546f0debb394f5ec","tid":46112,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔搵人</blockquote><br />\n我同佢只係返學時會打下招呼，唔係好熟，宜家都冇見成年半，都唔知send message同佢講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7bf7b234c2dd1d3c2d5583b818c6fd82494ae2","tid":46112,"uid":45949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"中二開始暗戀佢，期間都有拍過拖。<br />\n<br />\n已畢業後三年，始終都會掛住佢"},{"pid":"baa21d22cec60f46c4b7878f8a6be6b95f5b9612","tid":46112,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中二開始暗戀佢，期間都有拍過拖。<br />\n<br />\n已畢業後三年，始終都會掛住佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係中二開始"},{"pid":"b1d86b5e6ba78b5ce01693908aed10a51e4b8519","tid":46112,"uid":737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"反而係依家諗返起都解釋唔到點解當初會中意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697d24c0b50bad00e577bafece7e6dbf8af770a0","tid":46112,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而係依家諗返起都解釋唔到點解當初會中意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n荷爾蒙上腦冇得講嘅，但如果你過幾年都回味嘅，即係你真係好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}